OL,3,CThe war in the Gulf Britain can't
OL,4,Cescape
OL,6,FThe Israeli-US war with Iran threatens
OL,7,Fto trigger another wave of inflation,
OL,8,FITV News' Economics Editor Joel Hills
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FThe economy started the year with a
OL,12,Fwhimper.
OL,14,FBritain isn't in recession, but there
OL,15,Fwas little sign in January of the
OL,16,Fstrong growth the government promises
OL,17,Fthat would leave households feeling
OL,18,Fmaterially better off.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
