OL,3,CThe war in the Gulf Britain can't
OL,4,Cescape
OL,6,FAnd now the war in the Middle East
OL,7,Fthreatens to trigger another wave of
OL,8,Finflation, which would leave everyone
OL,9,Fin the UK poorer - including the
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,FAt Turner's Distribution in Norfolk,
OL,13,Fthe cost of filling its three thousand
OL,14,Florries has risen by #400,000 a week.
OL,16,FThose costs are already being passed
OL,17,Fon to its customers, who are
OL,18,Fsupermarkets, construction companies
OL,19,Fand petrol stations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
