OL,3,CThe war in the Gulf Britain can't
OL,4,Cescape
OL,6,FAnd eventually they will show up in
OL,7,Fthe prices consumers pay.
OL,9,FThe government cannot control global
OL,10,Fenergy prices. But it wants to be seen
OL,11,Fto be doing something, so it has asked
OL,12,Fthe competition watchdog to ensure
OL,13,Fpetrol retailers and energy suppliers
OL,14,Fare treating customers fairly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
