OL,3,CThe war in the Gulf Britain can't
OL,4,Cescape
OL,6,FThe Strait of Hormuz, one of the
OL,7,Fworld's most important energy routes,
OL,8,Fremains more or less closed off to
OL,9,Fshipping.
OL,11,FIn an attempt to contain prices, the
OL,12,FUnited States has said it will allow
OL,13,Fsome countries to buy Russian oil that
OL,14,Fhad previously been sanctioned.
OL,16,FThe United States is a major exporter
OL,17,Fof oil and gas and is therefore less
OL,18,Fexposed to the energy shock, but it is
OL,19,Fnot immune.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
