OL,3,CThe war in the Gulf Britain can't
OL,4,Cescape
OL,6,FPetrol prices are rising there too,
OL,7,Fand so are airline tickets.
OL,9,FWith mid-term elections approaching,
OL,10,Fthat is something voters are unlikely
OL,11,Fto ignore.
